### Development Setup

1. Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ohtaman/streamlit-desktop-app.git
```

2. Install dependencies:

```bash
cd src/aiopstack
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

3. Run Streamlit
```bash
streamlit run app.py
```


